        "TileImage": "$($repository 089f0a25-bd06-4139-8ef7-96e86a262302).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47. We have one more step before we know the identities and locations of the last Operation Skyfall lieutenant and the leader. It turns out the hackers you eliminated in Berlin only had the key to uncovering the data. The actual documents themselves are sealed in a data core in our facility in Chongqing, China.\r\rYou COULD just waltz in and retrieve the info, but their facility and ours have a bit of a history. It&apos;s hostile territory.\r\rNothing you can&apos;t handle, though. Good luck.",
